@DataBase PromptSequences.guide

@Index HBBS:Docs/Misc/Index.guide/MAIN

@Node Main "Prompt Sequences"

  Prompt Sequences
  ================

  Just use the following sequences below in a prompt and they will be replaced
  by some usefull data before the prompt is printed to the screen.

  {S}    BBS Name
  {C}    Current Conference Name (if use is in a conference)
  {H}    User's Handle (If logged on)
  {T}    Time in the format HH:MM
  {D}    Date, in the format DD/MMM/YYYY
  {E}    Ansi Control Sequence Introducer ( 'ESCAPE' +'[' )

@EndNode



